text: Dmitri Maneacov (born 6 March 1992) is a Moldovan footballer who plays as a forward for Moldovan club Spartanii Selemet. ==References== Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Moldovan footballers Category:Sportspeople from Bălți Category:Association football forwards Category:FC Zaria Bălți players Category:Moldovan National Division players
